snippet.title: Amber Scholl's #EXTRA Beauty Secrets | Vogue Parody
snippet.description:
HI ANGELS! WELCOME TO MY NEWEST FAKE VOGUE INTERVIEW LOL

Today I am sharing my weirdest and most extra beauty secrets in the form of my everyday makeup tutorial. It's everyday for me, but full dramatic prom glam for the average person lol. So here is a funny parody get ready with me Vogue style pretending to be a celebrity beauty guru lol.

I LOVE YOU! stay extra always.
3,150,000 kisses!
xx
Amber :)
